item.title: CVE-2023-23691|2024-08-02T10:35:33.687Z -- dell -- dell%20powervault%20me5
item.description: Dell EMC PV ME5, versions ME5.1.0.0.0 and ME5.1.0.1.0, contains a Client-side desync Vulnerability. An unauthenticated attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability to force a victim's browser to desynchronize its connection with the website, typically leading to XSS and DoS.
